          Home  Our Hotels  About Us  Peel for Business  Special Offers  Events Calendar  Join Our Mailing List  Contact Peel Group         Home    Our Hotels    Bull Hotel  Caledonian Hotel  Cosmopolitan Hotel  Crown & Mitre Hotel  George Hotel  King Malcolm Hotel  Midland Hotel  Norfolk Royale Hotel   Strathdon Hotel    Peel Hotels Locations Map            Welcome to Peel Hotels  Peel Hotels embodies all the traditional values of hotel keeping whilst keeping up to date with modern day requirements of the business and leisure traveller. Peel Hotels is majority owned by Robert and Charles Peel and as such a personal and dedicated approach is taken in terms of the comfort of all its guests. Client satisfaction is paramount and is the ethos of the Company together with the training and welfare of all its management and staff.  The Company owns nine Hotels throughout the United Kingdom, centrally located in their respective cities and towns. Each Hotel has its individual characteristic but all embody the desire to satisfy and exceed the expectations of our guests. We invest all our profits each year in the continual improvement of the quality and facilities of our Hotels and we are passionate in terms of the attention we pay to the overall maintenance and standards of cleanliness in all our Hotels.  Our philosophy is to be the local people's favourite hotel in each of our nine locations . In each Hotel, apart from providing excellent and up to date bedroom accommodation, we take an enormous interest in providing guests with contemporary menus in environments that are informal and relaxed. We relish the challenge of enticing our guests to want to eat at the Hotel rather than go out!  I hope you will enjoy our Hotels - see and appreciate the quality of our product and the friendliness of our management and staff and always make Peel Hotels your first choice when visiting the areas in which we are located.  Robert Peel Chairman  Back to top    Special Offers         Book 